Recently published, a Song by R. B. MAHAFFEY,, words by E. R. LATTA, entitled "WE SHOULD LOVE EACH OTHER MORE." Price 30 cents. Sales immense. The words and music are in such perfect harmony that it awakens, in those who hear it, a fond anticipation of a pure and happy home beyond the grave. Address R. B. MAHAFFEY, Publisher of Sheet Music and Music Books. ALTOONA, PA.
